The paper discusses the interaction between humans and swarms, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). It also discusses the use of autonomy and decision-making in the swarm, which relates to robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of system modelling techniques, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.MA).
